text: Ineta Ziemele (born 12 February 1970) is a judge from Latvia. She has been a judge at the European Court of Human Rights since April 27, 2005. She is President of the Fourth Section since 2012. == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian politicians Category:Judges of the European Court of Human Rights Category:Judges
